fix: continuation prompt was dumping last 4 task_messages (including assistant responses with thinking/tool_call tags) into a system message, causing them to render as raw text in the task UI. Removed history replay — the agent session already preserves context. Continuation now just says 'continue working' + highlights user responses if any. Also changed subtask creation from mandatory to suggested. Also moved ngl from compile-time cfg to runtime std::env::consts::ARCH check.
